{"_id":"a2af8b615584ccf6","name":"D-Scanner","type":"gear","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"itemType":"digivice","target":"tamer","timing":"passive","cost":{"digidollars":0,"realMoney":0,"special":"Loot only — cannot be purchased"},"quantity":1,"effect":"Must be equipped to digivolve your partner. Glows when wild or hostile Digimon are within 6 spaces. As a Free Action, scan one visible enemy to learn their Attribute and Element. As a Basic Action, perform a deep scan on one visible enemy to learn their Attribute, Element, and one combat stat of your choice. The D-Scanner supports digivolution up to Mega stage. Compatible with Spirit items — required to use any Legendary Spirit your Tamer carries.","isEquipped":false,"bonuses":{"courage":0,"friendship":0,"love":0,"knowledge":0,"sincerity":0,"reliability":0,"hope":0,"hpDamageReduction":0,"attackBonus":0,"damageBonus":0,"skillBonuses":{"blitz":0,"ironclad":0,"crusher":0,"ghost":0,"roar":0,"scan":0,"rally":0,"broadcast":0,"mend":0,"radar":0,"tame":0,"decode":0,"jackIn":0,"modify":0,"trace":0,"archive":0,"command":0,"playback":0,"firewall":0,"reinforce":0,"coreDrive":0,"zeroError":0,"fieldOps":0,"recovery":0}},"notes":"Required to use Legendary Spirits. Cap: Mega. Free Action: Attribute + Element. Basic Action: deep scan + 1 combat stat."}}
